data.text: The application imposes daily usage limitations on the GPT-4 AI, even for subscribers with unlimited access. Despite the AI's capabilities remaining unchanged, the app employs content censorship, lacks comprehensive formatting tools, and falls short in providing diverse writing styles and tones compared to Samsung's offering. Please note that the information provided is based on the knowledge cutoff of September 2021 and may be outdated. Additionally, the app currently lacks voice commands func
